<br>
FYI Im a 37 lvl Erudite mage first charcter so v untwinked. Wearing the Robe of Elements but saving up for crystline.<br>
<br>
Anyways joined a Giant group and got the toes for the first step. Gave in got shawl Hurah!<br>
<br>
Nxt night could not find a giant group so decided to solo the mines for exp and advertise to WTB Kromif heads. Mines are really good exp for this lvl btw once u get used to the pathing and spawns. Also keep the heads u get from the lesser tar goos they sell for big pp for High lvls needed giant faction. Just adversie /auction WTS Coldain head Increases faction with Giants when handed in and does not decrease dwarf faction. I sold 6 heads for 450pp total.<br>
