<br>
Go to thurgadin exchnage pottery vendors. making a side trip to get as much water as u can from Mordains measts. Buy 20 blocks of clay and 20 medim pots skethcs and combine 1 clay 1pot sketch and 1 water in pottery wheel. Drop the product on the floor u dont need it. This will very quicky get your skill from to 105 where i think it trivs. This is all u need to make the pottey implimnets used in this secion of quest.<br>
<br>
Ok the items u need to forage are Kodaik meat. 2 snow bunny meant and two ulthork meats.<br>
<br>
Kodaks where a brezze for me use normal pet+burn tactics and they die pretty sharp. Best place to find em is nxt to Draggon bridge in EW there is a shed load of spawns there.<br>
<br>
Bunnys. <br>
<br>
Now these are a pain i asked a our druid guildmaster who was in zone to wack a couple of em for me 2 kills 2 meat. But they do spawn everywhere so it should not be so much of a prob.<br>
<br>
Ulthorks.<br>
<br>
Bit harder but defiantly soloable. Run along the northern coast again the best place to find em. Use normal tactics and u shold be fine a couple cost me a full mana bar but i had a good book so...<br>
<br>
Anyway i wont explain all the niggly cooking bits as they are self explantory and im waffaing already the only think i will mention is u will need snake eggs for the dough for the ulthork meat pie. This is the only reason to leave Thurg.<br>
